<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWill1993"><a href="/wiki/Clifford_Will" title="Clifford Will" class="mw-redirect">Will, Clifford M.</a> (1993), <i>Was Einstein Right?</i>, Oxford University Press, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0192861700" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-286170-0</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Was+Einstein+Right%3F&amp;rft.aulast=Will&amp;rft.aufirst=Clifford+M.&amp;rft.au=Will%2C+Clifford+M.&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-19-286170-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Introduction_to_general_relativity"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWright2007">Wright, Ned (2007), <i><a href="http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~wright/cosmolog.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~wright/cosmolog.htm" rel="nofollow">Cosmology tutorial and FAQ</a></i>, University of California at Los Angeles<span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~wright/cosmolog.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~wright/cosmolog.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~wright/cosmolog.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved on 2007-06-12</span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Cosmology+tutorial+and+FAQ&amp;rft.aulast=Wright&amp;rft.aufirst=Ned&amp;rft.au=Wright%2C+Ned&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pub=University+of+California+at+Los+Angeles&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.astro.ucla.edu%2F%7Ewright%2Fcosmolog.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Introduction_to_general_relativity"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
